Here is the reproducible example (very educational ...):
----------------------------------------------------------
$ wget http://ehar.se/data/reex_0.1.1.tar.gz
$ R CMD INSTALL reex_0.1.1.tar.gz

{with "status = 1: blas/libblas.so.3, and lapack..}
